      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely pampered it, always keeping it garaged and making sure it stayed in pristine condition. There isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to message me with any questions!",
