      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully bulletproofed with Beisan components. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with Turner plates. The power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the signature tactile feedback this platform is known for. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero oxidation, while the interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the electronics. A truly turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
